data.description: Own a home-based business or enjoy riding 4 wheelers? The 10+/- acres consist of open pasture and beautiful trees surrounding the home and driveway, as well as 2 post lights in front yard. There are security lights on both front poles and two gated entrances for added safety. There is an enclosed back patio and 2 open concrete patios - one off master and another off opposite side of home. Behind home, there is a matching brick bonfire pit.  This beautiful home is 3/2/3.  The 3rd car offers a drive-thru access to the backyard, making it convenient for storing golf carts or Razor UTVs. This property has a flex room with added closet. The kitchen features Corian counters and custom cabinets. The primary bath includes a jacuzzi and double sinks, as well as large master closet. The house features a dining room and a separate breakfast nook. The kitchen is equipped with SS appliances. All entry doors, including those in shop, are insulated and equipped with storm doors with roll-down windows. In addition, there is a 30x50 (1500 sq/ft) insulated shop. The shop is wired for an alarm, satellite TV, high-speed internet, and phone. It also features a wood-burning stove, 6 large fluorescent overhead lights, 6 ceiling fans, heat/ac, speakers and surround sound wiring. There is an office/bedroom (approximately 10'X10') and a utility room (approximately 10'X10') with toilet, large tub sink, hot water tank, electricity, shower and w/d hookup. The shop also includes a 11x50 loafing shed attached. The home and shop garage doors are all insulated, and 2 solar roof exhaust fans on home. 2-car garage door on the front with a Wi-Fi-enabled opener, and a single-car garage door on the rear with 4 windows.  Overall, this property offers a perfect mix of amenities for those looking to enjoy both a comfortable living space and outdoor activities.  Located less than 10 minutes away from Walmart, approximately 15 minutes from BA, and approximately 20 minutes from downtown.
